7. EXPECTED OUTCOME

Better career decision-making.

Increased awareness of educational opportunities.

Improved alignment between student skills and industry requirements.

Enhanced employability through targeted skill development.

Personalized career planning support.



---

8. FUTURE ENHANCEMENTS

AI-powered Career Chatbot

Integration with Job Portals

Real-time Industry Trend Monitoring

