Advanced Predictive Analytics



---

9. CONCLUSION

The AI-Powered Career Guidance Website is a comprehensive platform that empowers students to make informed career decisions. By leveraging Artificial Intelligence, the system provides personalized guidance, identifies skill gaps, and recommends suitable educational and career pathways, helping students achieve their professional goals effectively.
